{"tid":1553051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝咁多位勇武手足保護我地全部人","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:15.000Z","uid":237943,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07ed392c9ec74db34a672a8f5d9b8ec761e02e3c","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"第一次開po 有錯屌得細力啲<br />\n真係忍唔住替啲勇武手足委屈<br />\n金次啲狗一邊宣佈左提早完結集會<br />\n一邊就封曬附近啲地鐵站<br />\n根本有曬預謀唔想比人走<br />\n成班大隊一路行<br />\n又話後面有狗追緊要跑<br />\n又話側面有狗落左車快走<br />\n又話地鐵站有狗衝緊上黎<br />\n一路上根本係令人憂心忡忡<br />\n但我發夢見到其實有好多勇武<br />\n企定定係度指引我地方向<br />\n有班仲係唔同地方set路障<br />\n果下覺得好安心<br />\n因為我地嘅後面係有班勇武幫我地斷後<br />\n可唔可以唔好再話set路障係鬼<br />\n佢地唔走係為左幫我地前面班人走<br />\n如果唔係佢地幫我地爭取時間<br />\n如果佢同我地大隊一齊走<br />\n我相信會好多和理非被捕<br />\n<br />\n唔該冷氣軍師屌人果陣自己落場睇下事實"},{"pid":"c89c2f1e1617b1331de775ff7d2cd1859d4e1972","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"係現場嘅人撫心自問<br />\n周圍都話有狗<br />\n其實個個都好驚<br />\n勇武仲要剋服呢個恐懼停留係原地"},{"pid":"a0aff37a89c9eba295d2511c30c50f5f7a392da8","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好多謝各位勇武<br />\n仲要成日比人屌"},{"pid":"df06fe4ead9f385a830553f450542700297376fc","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"cf95e6936de34e3003fcc566e343da51b2499583","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"5b23bfbb27b9f64b169ccdb1c4737ef950eda820","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"0491c2e0e5e865cf3df93a31f8963a3df47a16a6","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"6ac999debb5f055d8314baa2d4390c2dc8c45d2b","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"adad95398b1213a94886f792f8d4193c5e9a9b82","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"2d2d2b26d7300fb671ac1d02b52be69a54b7bca2","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"553a5f3786bb594a8f27df05ecf6440f107ac5f0","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"d56e7a40edd00def474a8de91989d51dea6812cf","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"f4da4953fe0e40c1bd0ab9f106e1f1ce434c472a","tid":1553051,"uid":237943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"推1"}]}